a.n: DON'T FORGET YOUR PASSPORT - VICTORIA, AUSTRALIA

p.k: Host Gordon Sivell takes in the colorful ANZAC parade in Melbourne, Australia and then tours the wine region of Yarra Valley after touring a unique wildlife facility designed to save indigenous wildlife with surgery. He takes a chopper flight over the 12 Apostles geological rock formations, cruises with the bottlenose dolphins and learns about aboriginal customs in a Victoria State sanctuary.
